  }, "Ethan Zuckerman"), ":"), mdx("p", null, "You mentioned earlier on in this interview that you were hoping to piss off as many people as possible. How's that going?"), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Tim Hwang"), ":"), mdx("p", null, "It's good. People are annoyed. And what's interesting is I would say that they're annoyed on both sides of the debate, which is maybe an intriguing thing and maybe it's a little orthogonal to what you're asking about. But on one hand you have ad tech people who are like, \"This guy's an idiot. He knows nothing.\" I was joking with someone earlier today. It's almost like debating with someone in a national security establishment because they're like, \"Oh, we know ads work, but we can't tell you anything that would prove that ", "[crosstalk 00:22:53]", ".\""), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
