    parentName: "p"
  }, "Tim Hwang"), ":"), mdx("p", null, "Exactly, you would agree with us. And that's totally a bit of rhetoric that I have seen. What's also really interesting is a response to the book, I would say even tech critics have not been happy with the book. And they've been not happy with the book in some ways because it subverts the narrative that this advertising infrastructure is a kind of mind control ray that has the ability to shape society in a very discreet manner. And so I guess everybody's sort of been pissed off, for what it's worth."), mdx("p", null, mdx("em", {
